            <h1 class="mb-3">Furniture Assembly Pricing Guide – FurnitureFix</h1>
            <p>Looking for <strong class="text-warning">affordable and professional furniture assembly in the UK</strong>? At FurnitureFix, we provide reliable, high-quality assembly services for a wide range of furniture items. Our goal is to make your life easier by delivering fast, efficient, and hassle-free service — all at <strong class="text-warning">competitive prices</strong>.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- How Our Pricing Works -->
    <section class="container my-5">
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow">
            <h2 class="mb-3">How Our Pricing Works</h2>
            <p>We understand that every piece of furniture is unique, so our pricing is designed to be <strong class="text-warning">transparent, flexible, and fair</strong>:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Per Item Pricing:</strong> We don’t charge by the hour. Instead, we agree on a fixed price for each item (or set of items) before we start, so there are no surprises.</li>
                <li><strong>Customised Approach:</strong> Every customer and piece of furniture is different. We assess the <strong>design, size, and complexity</strong> of your furniture and provide the <strong>best possible price</strong> tailored to your needs.</li>
                <li><strong>Clean-Up Included:</strong> After assembly, we make sure your space is tidy. <strong>No mess, no stress</strong>.</li>
                <li><strong>Discounts for Multiple Items:</strong> Got more than one item to assemble? We offer <strong>slight discounts</strong> for multiple items.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

